itemListElement.name: The Best Crispy Tofu

reviews.reviewBody: Didn’t crisp as well as hoped and flavor was a little bland though I might not have let it marinate long enough. Not bad but not great.

I don’t really like tofu but I am trying to go vegan mainly for health reasons it’s better for you I don’t think humans were created to digest meat. And since I have the last three months than vegan and shortly there after it’s amazing how much better you feel. A world of difference. That being saidI made this with no problem. I think it was probably the most I’ve ever enjoyed tofu. I did fry it a little longer then the recipe calls for. And I mixed a little peanut sauce with the tangy sweet-and-sour sauce for dipping. I also baked zucchini asparagus and carrots with vegan Parmesan cheese grated on top. And the coconut rice. It was an amazingly delicious meal. Thank you so much🥗🥗🥗🥗🥗🥗🙏🙏👍👍🥰🥰🥰
